      "text": "N Ahbräims nehine at-\nkat weenu Seeiwu/ Ke-\ntura Wahrdā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta dsemdeja winnam to\nSimronu/ un Jofsanu/ un Me-\ndanu/ un Midijann/ un Jiṣbakn/\nun Suū.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Jofsans dsemdinaja to\nSebn/ un Dedann/ un Dedana\nBehrni bija Afurim/ un Latusim/\nn Leünim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Midijana Behrni bija\nepa un Eewers/ un Anoks/ un\nlbidus/ un Eldaüs/ tchee wiṣṣi\nja Returas Behrni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Ahbräims deive wiṣ-\n/ kas tam peederreja Ihsää-\nm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet to Sahnu-Seeiwu\nsehneem/kas Ahbraimam bij/\nwe Ahbräims Dahwanas/ un\nstahdinaja tohs no fawa Deh-\nIhsääka/ wehl Dsihwś buh-\nms/ prett Rihteim us Au-\numa-Semint.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fchahś irr tahś Deenas\nGaddu tahś Dsihwibas Ah-\nāma/ zik ilgt tas Dsihwojis/\nts fepturdefinitś un peez Gad-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch iſtafde to Dweh-\n/ un Ahbräims nomirre tab-\nWezzuma/ wezz unn gann dsih-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nomirsī\nwojts/ un wiꞥſch tappe faweem\nLandim peepulzinahts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ihsääks un Ismaëls/\nwixxa Dehli aprakke winnu /\neeſsch tahś diwkahrtigas Bedres\nta Tihruma Gewrona/ Zōara ta\nGetitera Dehla/ kas prett Mam-\nre irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tai Tihrumā/ ko Ahbra-\näms pirzis bij no Etta Behrneem/\ntur irr Ahbräims aprakts/ un\nwinna Seeiva Sara.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pehz to/ kad Ahbra-\naims bij nomirris/ tad fwehtija\nDeews to Ihsaäku/ winna Deh-\nlu/ un Ihsaäks mitte pee ta Dsih-\nwaja Akkas/ kas mann usluhko.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee nu irr tee Raddu-\nRaksti Ismaëta / Ahbraima\nDehla/ ko Ahgare/ ta Egipterene/\nSaras Kalpone/ Ahbraimam irr\ndsemdejfi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un schee irr Ismaëta Behr-\nnu Wahrdi / ar faweemi Ziltut\nWahrdeem/Ismaëta Pirmdsim-\ntajs / Nebajots un Redars/ un\nAdbeels/ un Mibsams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Misimus/ un Dumus/\nun Masus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Adars un Temus/ Je-\nturs/ Nawis/ un Kedmus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schee irr Ismaëta Behr-\nni/ un schee irr winno Wahrdi/\npehz winno Muischahm un Dil-\nlmi/diwpadefinitśWirtneeki pahr\nfaweem Gaudim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un schee irr Ismaëta Dsih-\nwibas Gaddi/ ſunits trihsdefmits\nun feptin Gaddi / un wiꞥſch ig-\nlaide fawn Dwehfeli/ un nomir-\n"
    }
  ],
